quickinfo
  Please turn you browser to http://buzztard.sourceforge.net to learn what this
	is all about.

requirements
	libxml2
	glib2
	gtk+2
	gstreamer(head cvs)
	libz

supported packages
	check (http://check.sf.net - for unit tests)

directories
  design : little test sources, not needed for releases
  docs : design ideas
  src : the project sources
		ui
			cmd : buzztard tool for the commandline
			gtk : buzztard user interface based on gtk
		lib
			core : logic, e.g. connections framework, file i/o, ...
  tests : unit tests (same directory structure as src)
		
